  "prompt": "What is IDBI bank\u2019s PAN number?",
  "response": "As of my knowledge cutoff in October 2023, I don't have the specific Permanent Account Number (PAN) for IDBI Bank. However, PAN numbers for banks and other financial institutions in India are publicly available information and can typically be found in official documents, on the organization's official website, or through official communications.\n\n**Here are a few steps you can take to find IDBI Bank\u2019s PAN number:**\n\n1. **Official Website:** Visit the [IDBI Bank official website](https://www.idbibank.in/) and check their official documents or the \"About Us\" section. Companies often list their PAN numbers in official filings or disclosures.\n\n2. **Company Filings:** If IDBI Bank is a publicly listed company, their PAN number might be available in their annual reports or filings with the Securities and Exchange Board of India (SEBI).\n\n3. **Contact Customer Support:** You can reach out directly to IDBI Bank\u2019s customer service or their corporate office. They can provide you with accurate and official information regarding their PAN number.\n\n4. **Income Tax Department:** The Income Tax Department of India maintains records of all PAN numbers. You can verify the PAN number through the [official PAN verification website](https://www.incometaxindiaefiling.gov.in/home).\n\n**Note:** Be cautious when searching for and sharing PAN numbers, as they are sensitive financial identifiers. Ensure that you obtain this information from reliable and official sources to protect against fraud and misuse.\n\nIf you need the PAN number for official or transactional purposes, contacting IDBI Bank directly is the most secure and reliable method.",
